{"ts":"2026-06-26T08:08:51.069Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_end","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Developing the Presentation**\n\nI've crafted a really amazing \"Terms of Service & SLA Guide\" complete with live selection for sandbox, foundry, and factory compute parameters! I've included beautiful icons and layouts to make it visually engaging and easy to use. I'm now setting my sights on the next task!\n\n\n**Refining the NDA Workflow**\n\nI'm now focusing on the NDA process and making it top-notch! I want to enhance `app/nda/page.tsx` with a premium aesthetic and interactive elements. Specifically, I'm thinking of an animated background grid, a dynamic timeline of the automated draft, and a visual representation of the \"Digital Signature Enclave\" to show secure IP context. The form will be fully responsive and modern, with validation and loading feedback. Keeping the code around 4000-5000 chars is my target.\n\n\n**Designing the Implementation**\n\nI'm now drafting the React code for `app/nda/page.tsx`, aiming for a premium, clean design. This version features an `AnimatedBackgroundGrid`, a custom interactive visual for the NDA pipeline, high-fidelity step cards, and a glassmorphic form. I'm measuring the character count as I go.\n\n\n**Defining the Agreement Stages**\n\nI'm now outlining the steps of the NDA process. Step one involves submitting the corporate legal name and preferred jurisdiction. Next, I'll describe how a compliance parser creates a mutual NDA draft. Finally, the user will be able to execute digital signatures and securely seal the shared context. I'm focusing on crafting a clear and concise user flow.\n\n\n**Prioritizing IP Protection**\n\nI'm now zeroing in on the 'Two-Way Intellectual Property Vault' aspect of the NDA. This involves focusing on reciprocal protection, which highlights the need for a mutual agreement to safeguard proprietary codebases, vector weights, models, and credentials. The goal is to ensure robust security.\n\n\n**Visualizing the Signature**\n\nI'm now integrating a \"Trust Enclave Signature\" visualization, using a dynamic display for the active jurisdiction. The goal is a clear, instantly understandable representation of the compliance kernel. I want to convey that this is secure, with an emphasis on clarity and trust, within the modern design.\n\n\n**Constructing the Step Cards**\n\nI'm currently working on building the individual step cards for the NDA process. I'm focusing on making them visually appealing and informative, using a clean design with clear headings and descriptions. My goal is to create an easy-to-follow and engaging user experience.\n\n\n**Refining the Submission**\n\nI'm now refining the submission process within the NDA workflow, focusing on the visual and functional aspects of the initial submission step. I'm aiming for a concise and easy-to-understand form with clear prompts and validation. I'm thinking about including a success message with clear next steps after successful submission. The goal is to make the submission process as smooth and intuitive as possible.\n\n\n**Improving the Interface**\n\nI'm now iterating on the initial submission form within the NDA workflow. I've focused on two key fields: corporate legal name and authorized officer email, both of which are required. I'm aiming for a visually clean and intuitive experience for the user. I have refined the design of the form elements and included placeholders and labels for clarity, with validation for all inputs.\n\n\n"}}
{"ts":"2026-06-26T08:08:51.085Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"editor","toolCallId":"rihfoq6k","input":{"path":"/Users/ayushbansal/Documents/GitHub/hirezapp_landing_page/app/nda/page.tsx","old_text":"\"use client\";\n\nimport React, { useState } from \"react\";\nimport InnerPageShell from \"@/components/inner-pages/InnerPageShell\";\nimport InnerPageHero from \"@/components/inner-pages/InnerPageHero\";\nimport PremiumCTA from \"@/components/inner-pages/PremiumCTA\";\nimport { Lock, CheckCircle2, Send } from \"lucide-react\";\n\nexport default function NdaPage() {\n  const [submitted, setSubmitted] = useState(false);\n  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false);\n\n  const steps = [\n    { num: \"01\", title: \"Initiate Request\", desc: \"Submit your corporate legal name and Preferred Jurisdictional settings.\" },\n    { num: \"02\", title: \"Automated Draft\", desc: \"Our compliance parser compiles a standardized Mutual NDA tailored to your region.\" },\n    { num: \"03\", title: \"Execute & Lock\", desc: \"Digital signatures are completed. All shared contexts are sealed in enclaves.\" }\n  ];\n\n  return (\n    <InnerPageShell>\n      <InnerPageHero\n        category=\"Legal & Compliance\"\n        title=\"Mutual NDA Protocol\"\n        highlightedWord=\"Protocol\"\n        description=\"Learn how GFF AI secures early-stage sandbox investigations, safeguards proprietary designs, and executes mutual non-disclosure agreements.\"\n      />\n\n      <div className=\"max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-16 pb-24 space-y-12 relative z-10\">\n        <div className=\"p-6 rounded-[24px] border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/60 backdrop-blur-[12px] space-y-3\">\n          <h2 className=\"text-[18px] font-semibold text-white tracking-tight flex items-center gap-2\">\n            <Lock className=\"w-4 h-4 text-[#E4000F]\" /> Reciprocal Confidentiality Protection\n          </h2>\n          <p className=\"text-white/70 leading-relaxed text-[13px] font-light\">\n            Before we demonstrate bespoke multi-agent sandboxes or evaluate database schemas in our Garage phase, GFF AI secures reciprocal confidentiality. Our Mutual NDA is engineered to safeguard proprietary codebases, vector weights, model parameters, and corporate credentials.\n          </p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\">\n          {steps.map((step, idx) => (\n            <div key={idx} className=\"p-6 rounded-[24px] border border-white/5 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#08080a] to-[#010101] relative overflow-hidden group\">\n              <span className=\"absolute top-4 right-4 text-[42px] font-mono font-bold leading-none text-white/5\">{step.num}</span>\n              <h4 className=\"text-[15px] font-semibold text-white tracking-tight mt-2\">{step.title}</h4>\n              <p className=\"mt-2 text-[12px] leading-relaxed text-white/50 font-light\">{step.desc}</p>\n            </div>\n          ))}\n        </div>\n\n        <div className=\"p-6 rounded-[24px] border border-white/5 bg-[#030304]/80 max-w-xl mx-auto space-y-4\">\n          <div className=\"space-y-1 text-center\">\n            <span className=\"inline-flex px-2.5 py-0.5 text-[9px] font-mono tracking-widest text-[#009DFF] border border-[#009DFF]/25 bg-[#009DFF]/5 rounded-full uppercase\">Request Portal</span>\n            <h3 className=\"text-[18px] font-semibold text-white tracking-tight\">Initiate Mutual NDA Draft</h3>\n          </div>\n\n          {submitted ? (\n            <div className=\"py-6 text-center space-y-3\">\n              <CheckCircle2 className=\"w-10 h-10 text-green-500 mx-auto\" />\n              <p className=\"text-white/80 text-[13px] font-light\">Our legal team will email your custom bilateral NDA draft to the specified address within 4 business hours.</p>\n            </div>\n          ) : (\n            <form onSubmit={(e) => { e.preventDefault(); setLoading(true); setTimeout(() => { setLoading(false); setSubmitted(true); }, 1000); }} className=\"space-y-3\">\n              <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3\">\n                <input required placeholder=\"Corporate Legal Name\" className=\"w-full px-4 py-2 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/60 text-[12px] text-white focus:outline-none\" />\n                <input type=\"email\" required placeholder=\"Authorized Officer Email\" className=\"w-full px-4 py-2 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/60 text-[12px] text-white focus:outline-none\" />\n              </div>\n              <select className=\"w-full px-4 py-2 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/60 text-[12px] text-white/80 focus:outline-none\">\n                <option>Delaware, United States</option>\n                <option>England & Wales</option>\n                <option>Singapore (SGX Compliant)</option>\n              </select>\n              <button type=\"submit\" className=\"w-full py-2.5 rounded-xl text-[12px] font-semibold text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-[#E4000F] to-[#009DFF] hover:opacity-95 flex items-center justify-center gap-1.5\">\n                {loading ? \"Processing Secure Ticket...\" : <><Send className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" /> Request NDA Review</>}\n              </button>\n            </form>\n          )}\n        </div>\n\n        <PremiumCTA\n          title=\"Preparing for an architectural audit session?\"\n          description=\"Schedule a technical workspace review to understand how your proprietary parameters are compartmentalized within private sandboxes.\"\n          primaryLabel=\"Contact Legal Desk\"\n          primaryHref=\"/contact?pathway=nda\"\n          secondaryLabel=\"Review Trust Specs\"\n          secondaryHref=\"/privacy\"\n        />\n      </div>\n    </InnerPageShell>\n  );\n}","new_text":"\"use client\";\n\nimport React, { useState } from \"react\";\nimport InnerPageShell from \"@/components/inner-pages/InnerPageShell\";\nimport InnerPageHero from \"@/components/inner-pages/InnerPageHero\";\nimport PremiumCTA from \"@/components/inner-pages/PremiumCTA\";\nimport AnimatedBackgroundGrid from \"@/components/inner-pages/AnimatedBackgroundGrid\";\nimport { Lock, CheckCircle2, Send, ShieldCheck } from \"lucide-react\";\n\nexport default function NdaPage() {\n  const [submitted, setSubmitted] = useState(false);\n  const [loading, setLoading] = useState(false);\n  const [jurisdiction, setJurisdiction] = useState(\"Delaware, United States\");\n\n  const steps = [\n    { num: \"01\", title: \"Initiate Request\", desc: \"Submit your corporate legal name and preferred jurisdictional settings.\" },\n    { num: \"02\", title: \"Automated Draft\", desc: \"Our compliance parser compiles a standardized Mutual NDA tailored to your region.\" },\n    { num: \"03\", title: \"Execute & Lock\", desc: \"Digital signatures are completed. All shared contexts are sealed in enclaves.\" }\n  ];\n\n  const handleRequest = (e: React.FormEvent) => {\n    e.preventDefault();\n    setLoading(true);\n    setTimeout(() => {\n      setLoading(false);\n      setSubmitted(true);\n    }, 1200);\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <InnerPageShell>\n      <div className=\"relative overflow-hidden min-h-screen pb-16\">\n        <AnimatedBackgroundGrid />\n\n        <InnerPageHero\n          category=\"Legal & Compliance\"\n          title=\"Mutual NDA Protocol\"\n          highlightedWord=\"Protocol\"\n          description=\"Learn how GFF AI secures early-stage sandbox investigations, safeguards proprietary designs, and executes mutual non-disclosure agreements.\"\n        />\n\n        <div className=\"max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-16 pb-24 space-y-12 relative z-10\">\n          \n          <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-center p-8 rounded-[24px] border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/60 backdrop-blur-[12px]\">\n            <div className=\"lg:col-span-7 space-y-4\">\n              <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-[#E4000F]\">\n                <Lock className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n                <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono tracking-[0.2em] uppercase font-bold\">Reciprocal Protection</span>\n              </div>\n              <h2 className=\"text-[22px] sm:text-[28px] font-bold text-white tracking-tight\">Two-Way Intellectual Property Vault</h2>\n              <p className=\"text-white/70 leading-relaxed text-[13.5px] font-light font-sans\">\n                Before evaluating database schemas, system APIs, or launching multi-agent sandboxes in our Garage phase, we establish bilateral legal protection. Our Mutual NDA is engineered to safeguard proprietary codebases, vector weights, models, and corporate credentials under premium security.\n              </p>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div className=\"lg:col-span-5 p-6 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/40 space-y-4\">\n              <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n                <ShieldCheck className=\"w-8 h-8 text-[#009DFF]\" />\n                <div>\n                  <h4 className=\"text-[14px] font-semibold text-white\">Trust Enclave Signature</h4>\n                  <p className=\"text-[11.5px] text-white/55\">Governed by standard compliance kernels.</p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <div className=\"p-3 bg-white/5 rounded-lg border border-white/5\">\n                <div className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/40 uppercase\">Active Jurisdiction</div>\n                <div className=\"text-[13px] text-white font-medium mt-0.5\">{jurisdiction}</div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\">\n            {steps.map((step, idx) => (\n              <div key={idx} className=\"p-6 rounded-[24px] border border-white/5 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#08080a] to-[#010101] relative overflow-hidden group\">\n                <span className=\"absolute top-4 right-4 text-[42px] font-mono font-bold leading-none text-white/5\">{step.num}</span>\n                <h4 className=\"text-[15px] font-semibold text-white tracking-tight mt-2\">{step.title}</h4>\n                <p className=\"mt-2 text-[12px] leading-relaxed text-white/50 font-light\">{step.desc}</p>\n              </div>\n            ))}\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"p-8 rounded-[24px] border border-white/5 bg-[#030304]/80 max-w-xl mx-auto space-y-6 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden\">\n            <div className=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-[120px] h-[120px] bg-gradient-to-bl from-[#009DFF]/10 to-transparent rounded-full blur-2xl pointer-events-none\" />\n            <div className=\"space-y-1 text-center\">\n              <span className=\"inline-flex px-2.5 py-0.5 text-[9px] font-mono tracking-widest text-[#009DFF] border border-[#009DFF]/25 bg-[#009DFF]/5 rounded-full uppercase\">Request Portal</span>\n              <h3 className=\"text-[20px] font-semibold text-white tracking-tight\">Initiate Mutual NDA Draft</h3>\n            </div>\n\n            {submitted ? (\n              <div className=\"py-8 text-center space-y-4\">\n                <CheckCircle2 className=\"w-12 h-12 text-green-500 mx-auto\" />\n                <h4 className=\"text-[16px] font-semibold text-white\">Draft Initiated Successfully</h4>\n                <p className=\"text-white/60 text-[13px] font-light max-w-xs mx-auto\">\n                  Our legal team will compile and dispatch your custom bilateral Mutual NDA draft to the authorized address within 4 business hours.\n                </p>\n              </div>\n            ) : (\n              <form onSubmit={handleRequest} className=\"space-y-4\">\n                <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n                  <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                    <label className=\"text-[10px] uppercase text-white/40 tracking-wider\">Corporate Legal Name</label>\n                    <input required placeholder=\"Acme Corp LLC\" className=\"w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/60 text-[13px] text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-white/10\" />\n                  </div>\n                  <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                    <label className=\"text-[10px] uppercase text-white/40 tracking-wider\">Authorized Officer Email</label>\n                    <input type=\"email\" required placeholder=\"officer@acme.com\" className=\"w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/60 text-[13px] text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-white/10\" />\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                  <label className=\"text-[10px] uppercase text-white/40 tracking-wider\">Preferred Jurisdiction</label>\n                  <select \n                    value={jurisdiction} \n                    onChange={(e) => setJurisdiction(e.target.value)}\n                    className=\"w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/60 text-[13px] text-white/80 focus:outline-none focus:border-white/10\"\n                  >\n                    <option>Delaware, United States</option>\n                    <option>England & Wales</option>\n                    <option>Singapore (SGX Compliant)</option>\n                  </select>\n                </div>\n\n                <button type=\"submit\" className=\"w-full py-3 rounded-xl text-[12px] font-mono uppercase tracking-wider font-bold text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-[#E4000F] to-[#009DFF] hover:opacity-95 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 transition-all shadow-[0_4px_20px_rgba(228,0,15,0.15)]\">\n                  {loading ? \"Compiling Custom Ticket...\" : <><Send className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" /> Request NDA Review</>}\n                </button>\n              </form>\n            )}\n          </div>\n\n          <PremiumCTA\n            title=\"Preparing for an architectural audit session?\"\n            description=\"Schedule a technical workspace review to understand how your proprietary parameters are compartmentalized within private sandboxes.\"\n            primaryLabel=\"Contact Legal Desk\"\n            primaryHref=\"/contact?pathway=nda\"\n            secondaryLabel=\"Review Trust Specs\"\n            secondaryHref=\"/privacy\"\n          />\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </InnerPageShell>\n  );\n}\n"}}}
